One Policeman Dead After Gun Attack on Erdogan Convoy, NTV Says

-- B y   M a r k   B e n t l e y
-- 
2011-05-04T15:00:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-04/one-policeman-dead-after-gun-attack-on-erdogan-convoy-ntv-says.html
One policeman died after men threw a
bomb and opened fire on a police convoy that had been protecting
Prime Minister  Recep Tayyip Erdogan  in northern  Turkey  today,
NTV news channel reported.  The convoy was attacked on a mountain road in the Kastamonu
province after Erdogan departed the area, NTV said. Erdogan was
in Kastamonu for a public rally ahead of the June 12 general
election.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mark Bentley at 
 mbentley3@bloomberg.net  